# Wick — Code Owners
#
# Each category in packages/CATEGORIES.md is owned by one squad. Pull requests
# touching files inside a category automatically request review from that squad.
#
# Replace the @wick/* placeholder teams with real GitHub teams or usernames as
# the org grows. Until then, all teams are aliased to @astralchemist as the
# sole maintainer.
#
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones. Always end with the
# most specific overrides at the bottom.

